==English==
===Etymology===
From the name of the eponymous character in the television program ''[[w:MacGyver|MacGyver]]'', a [[secret agent]] with an [[uncanny]] ability to [[construct]] [[weapon]]s from seemingly useless bits of [[junk]].

===Adjective===
'''MacGyvered'''

#{{idiom}} (''informal'') [[hastily]] assembled from spare parts, to use unsuitable items to construct something.